---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { companyName } from '../content/site';
---

<Layout
  locale="en"
  title={`Privacy | ${companyName}`}
  description="Privacy policy for the BenchTrust pre-launch landing page."
  path="/privacy/"
  alternatePath="/datenschutz/"
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24 text-slate-200 md:px-10">
    <div class="panel-surface rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-12">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-cyan-300/80">BenchTrust GmbH i.G.</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-4xl text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-base leading-8 text-slate-300">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">1. Privacy at a glance</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">We take the protection of your personal data very seriously. When you use our pre-launch website (benchtrust.com / benchtrust.de) and sign up for our waitlist, various personal data is collected. This privacy policy explains what data we collect, what we use it for and on what legal basis.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">2. Controller</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Data processing on this website is carried out by the website operator:</p>
          <p class="mt-2">BenchTrust GmbH i.G.<br />Lange Strasse 75, 76530 Baden-Baden, Germany<br />Email: contact@benchtrust.com</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">3. Data collection on our website (the waitlist)</h2>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong class="text-white">Type of data:</strong> When you sign up for our early access / waitlist, we collect your name, business email address and your stated role (buyer or provider).</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong class="text-white">Purpose:</strong> We use this data exclusively to inform you about the launch of our platform in June 2026, to grant you early access ("sneak peeks") and to prepare your future profile accurately.</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong class="text-white">Legal basis:</strong> Processing of this data is based on your consent (Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR). You may withdraw your consent at any time (e.g. by clicking "Unsubscribe" in our emails or by emailing us). The lawfulness of processing carried out before the withdrawal remains unaffected.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">4. Use of HubSpot (CRM &amp; forms)</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">We use HubSpot for our waitlist and email communication. The provider is HubSpot, Inc., 25 First Street, 2nd Floor, Cambridge, MA 02141 USA (or HubSpot European Settlement for EU citizens).</p>
          <p class="mt-2">The data you enter in the waitlist form is stored on HubSpot's servers. HubSpot helps us manage our launch campaign and assign sign-ups to roles (buyer/provider). We have concluded a data processing agreement (DPA) with HubSpot, ensuring that our website visitors' data is processed only according to our instructions and in compliance with the GDPR.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">5. Hosting (Vercel)</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Our static pre-launch website is hosted by Vercel Inc. When you visit our site, the host automatically collects technical connection data (e.g. IP address, browser type, time) to deliver the page reliably and securely (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR).</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">6. Your rights</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">You have the right at any time to obtain free information about the origin, recipients and purpose of your stored personal data. You also have the right to request the correction, blocking or deletion of this data. Please contact us at the address stated above.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <a class="mt-10 inline-flex rounded-full border border-white/15 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:border-cyan-300/60 hover:text-cyan-200" href="/">
        Back to homepage
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>